{"tid":1796823,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩工可以hea到退休介","createTime":"2019-12-25T01:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T13:42:37.000Z","uid":35284,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2adaae319de051b5ea1fa361512435ddd90d60","tid":1796823,"uid":35284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"成日見有人話自己返工冇野做 <br />\n日日做自己野hea到收工 <br />\n但人工又可以高到17-20k都有 未做過真係好難相信<br />\n小妹依家返緊個份都係17k 但做到個人半死咁<br />\n最近心態改變咗 我意識到自己根本唔等錢洗<br />\n唔知咁辛苦為咩 我唔拍拖唔結婚生仔<br />\n最緊要唔洗供樓同交租 我唔介意人工低<br />\n想有返啲生活 同私人時間<br />\n我係唔上進冇大志 只係唔想太辛苦 <br />\n做保安我又怕悶 去投注站做清潔呀姐都幾好似唔錯<br />\n我既志願係成為一個廢青 每日食玩訓 一路廢到老"},{"pid":"5e8606395792b001d3f3ea3fd7875ea1ba97ac1a","tid":1796823,"uid":58630,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T01:56:03.000Z","msg":"當你捱到成為老屎忽嗰日咪可以hea到退休囉"},{"pid":"54da798462a352018c7342df97164089cb2b6ce4","tid":1796823,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:01:32.000Z","msg":"不如講下自己咩學歷咩能力先"},{"pid":"7bb9a79f71b4c954da8826bf9ba88e745d0c1977","tid":1796823,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:02:42.000Z","msg":"Son"},{"pid":"53627fcecfabf9f0eebdc5a749f9087e20923df8","tid":1796823,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:02:54.000Z","msg":"黑警好多ot<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Q1r0hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Q1r0hf.jpg&h=9a7a8779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEwjAQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEwjAQA.jpg&h=13efda79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd87e0309c54b032c28348034f4172d9eadbaa61","tid":1796823,"uid":103362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"拎綜援啦，即刻財務自由"},{"pid":"7b009489ce36e7a4a38cf74c31f8c03cc08df110","tid":1796823,"uid":3302,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-